PROGRAM-ID. MyProgram.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 CUSTOMER-RECORD.
   05 CUSTOMER-NAME    PIC X(20).
   05 CUSTOMER-AGE     PIC 9(2).
   05 CUSTOMER-SALARY  PIC 9(5)V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
   MOVE "John Doe" TO CUSTOMER-NAME.
   MOVE 30 TO CUSTOMER-AGE.
   MOVE 2500.50 TO CUSTOMER-SALARY.

   DISPLAY "Before Initialize: ".
   DISPLAY "Name: " CUSTOMER-NAME.
   DISPLAY "Age: " CUSTOMER-AGE.
   DISPLAY "Salary: " CUSTOMER-SALARY.

   INITIALIZE CUSTOMER-RECORD.

   DISPLAY "After Initialize: ".
   DISPLAY "Name: " CUSTOMER-NAME.
   DISPLAY "Age: " CUSTOMER-AGE.
   DISPLAY "Salary: " CUSTOMER-SALARY.

   STOP RUN.
